The Telegraph - Calcutta : Bengal

Archives
				 Governor path 

																								Calcutta, Dec. 7: Governor Gopalkrishna Gandhi told a symposium today there should be a balance between industry and agriculture. 
																								Within agriculture also, there should be a balance between the use of chemicals, fertilisers and organic bio-farming. The future of our progress lies in the balance, he said at the Central Glass and Ceramic Research Institute.

